8. Intro to Executor Service
-> multithreading wali api ko ham bolte hai concurrency api
-> Executor service isliye aaya hai ki apna OS jo hai wo bolta tha ki aap thread banao
or chalaunga or marunga bar bar wo chala ta tha or mar ta tha to isme jyad mhenat
lag raha tha to isko solve karne aaya apna
--> Executor sevice apna thread pool banata hai jha pe wo apne thread ka group rhak
ta hai jise ham pool bhi khete hai executor service nazar rhak ta hai ki konsa thread
khali bheta hai or konsa kaam kar rha hai
-> jitne thread ka ham pool bana ke rhakenge wo kabhi bhi marenge nahi bhale hi khali
bhete rhaenge but marenge nhai
-> jab bhi ham Executor service ko koi task(kaam) dete hai to wo task queue ke andar
rhak tha hai and wait karta hai ki kab mera thread pool me se koi bhi thread khali hoga
and me apne task queue me se first task uss thread ko dedu or wo thread mera
task run karde QUEUE (first in first out)
-> application wala apne code hai implements runnable wale code task queue ko de dega
and task queue hai wo code thread pool ke khali wale thread ko dedega
->Executor service banate shamy ham usko abata denge ki kitne thread ke shaat bana na hai
and bass usko task dete rhaenge and thread pool chala ta rhaega

